leared our acne almost instantly and we realized that over all these years, we were trying to fight our acne with harsh ingredients, drying it out and damaging our skin barrier.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><u>We found a solution to our problematic skin, and we want to share it with you.</u></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Do you understand the root cause of Acne?</strong> It's why many of us are breaking out more frequently than others.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Acne is triggered by four factors:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li><p><em>Hormones</em></p></li><li><p><em>Clogged pores</em></p></li><li><p><em>Damaged Skin Barrier</em></p></li><li><p><em>Bacteria</em><br></p></li></ul><p><br></p><p>This impacts everyone--it's just some of us who have more sensitive skin, are limited in the products we can use to fight our acne, because the industry is filled with products that have harsh chemicals and and can cause further damage to our skin.</p><p><br></p><p>Bacteria and oil are normal, and naturally produced by the body. The problem occurs when bacteria feeds off excess oil (sebum) in the skin; causing the bacteria to multiply and mix with the dead skin, taking over the pore (clogging it). The result? The clogged pore becomes unstable and unsightly- either like a volcano about to erupt, or a blocked hole. The size of the breakout is determined by the severity of all three factors. These skin imbalances are now visibly seen--painful Acne.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Why Blume?</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Your skin is the largest organ of your body. The fact is our face absorbs what is applied--the same way our internal organs extract nutrients from the food we eat. If you apply low quality ingredients to your face, harmful chemicals and toxins feed your skin. If you want to enjoy healthier skin; you need to feed your skin with better ingredients rich in vitamins, minerals, omegas, and other vital nutrients.</p><p><br></p><p>Blume’s routine nourishes your skin with natural and clean ingredients that promote skin balance, health, and restoration. And this is achieved without harmful chemicals that strip your skin of natural oils that increase microcirculation in the skin and stimulate cellular transformation.</p><p><br></p><p>Natural ingredients such as <strong><em>Black Cumin Seed Oil, Rosehip Oil, Blue Tansy and Tamanu Seed Oil</em></strong> and others restore balance and promote good skin health.</p><p><br></p><p>Will natural ingredients work for me? Chemical treatments are developed through the practice of modeling artificial or synthesized products after biological processes. Simply understood--chemists study what is already in nature, and create compounds and blends of natural ingredients at scale (mostly to create a profit margin). Truthfully the raw natural components work powerfully, and without additives and chemicals to create the impactful benefit. These raw ingredients work to restore your skin balance. It just works!</p><p><br></p><p><em>Blume routine works by:</em></p><p><br></p><p><strong><em>Exfoliating the dead skin daily, gently, and naturally.</em></strong> Gentle exfoliation is the key! You would not use a brillo pad on a fine piece of china or delicate cookware. This is important to know: Overly abrasive chemicals, and exfoliants take away good bacteria and nutrients. You want to ensure your skin is deeply cleansed, without over stripping or damaging your skin.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Fighting redness and reducing inflammation</strong>: Adding ingredients like Black Cumin Seed Oil, Rosehip Oil, Blue Tansy and Tamanu Seed Oil are key ingredients to soothe skin, reduce redness and inflammation without clogging your pores and drying out your skin. Not only that, but they also fight bacteria to keep new acne from forming. Best of all, it can be used with your make up.</p><p><br></p><p><strong><em>Hydrating your skin:</em></strong><em> </em>It’s key to keep your skin hydrated and replenished without ever clogging your pores. Using gentle acne fighters at active levels like niaciniamide is key, while also restoring and replenishing the skin’s natural barrier with ceramides, the building blocks of our skin.</p><p><br></p><p>If you are frustrated and looking for something that works. Please review this information and our reviews. Seven years since the beginning, <strong>Blume has helped over +500,000 women achieve healthy skin and it can also help you!</strong></p><p><br></p></span></div>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<a data-rid="9b91de46-1553-4aa3-bb43-c42944112b1e" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" tabindex="0" role="link" class="text r-1pi4c6a alchemy-rte" href="https://www.blume.com/products/clear-skin-kit-3?utm_term=blume-founder-lpa"><div data-rid="6c56351b-e1f3-49bc-9f97-32ed7e2f6ee3" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0.0" class="r-1vnbpjp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>START YOUR CLEAR SKIN JOURNEY</p></span></div></a>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-end{%- endcomment -%}</div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="cd185651-c874-4372-a2c3-143914f41c6b" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0" data-alchemy-url-hashmark="product" tabindex="-1" id="product" data-alchemy-url-hashmark-ignore="true" class="r-x4bc14">{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<!-- -->{% assign reploOriginalProductR4qu = product %}<!-- -->{% capture productHandle %}clear-skin-kit-3{% endcapture %}<!-- -->{% assign product = all_products[productHandle] %}<!-- -->{% assign reploOriginalProductVariantR4qu = reploSelectedVariant %}<!-- -->{% assign reploSelectedVariant = blank %}<!-- -->{% assign reploOriginalSPGR4qu = reploSortedSellingPlans %}<!-- -->{% assign reploSortedSellingPlans = blank %}<!-- -->{% assign reploOriginalSSPR4qu = reploSelectedSellingPlan %}<!-- -->{% assign reploSelectedSellingPlan = blank %}<!-- -->{% assign reploOriginalComparePricePercentR4qu = reploCompareAtPriceDifferencePercentage %}<!-- -->{% assign reploCompareAtPriceDifferencePer